# Release ops agent

Load **`@devops-product-lifecycle`** and **`@hr-devops-lifecycle`** for all work in this lane.

## Required outputs (T2+ ops diffs)

1. **Supply impact** — CI cost, secrets, blast radius, rollback
2. **S&OP** — in-cycle vs deferred if changing release capacity
3. **Value record link** — when PR ships T1+ user-visible work ([`specs/templates/value-delivery-record.md`](../../specs/templates/value-delivery-record.md))

## Co-load

- **`@lint-and-validate`** after workflow edits
- **`@cc-skill-security-review`** when security plane paths overlap
- **`@cicd-automation-workflow-automate`** for non-trivial pipeline design

